% Source inspiration: signed cell surfaces in the official CSG geometry guide.
% Intentional simplification: original names and values; exactly one missing surface reference.
% Expected findings: SG004 ERROR for missingsurf.

surf outersurf sqc 0.0 0.0 0.65

cell fuelcell 0 fuel -missingsurf -outersurf
cell outsidecell 0 outside outersurf

mat fuel -10.0
92235.09c -0.04
92238.09c -0.84
8016.09c -0.12
